{"tid":705670,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該分手？","createTime":"2018-06-17T11:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T11:50:49.000Z","uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b361fe8418919bfc65301a20866a2009deee81cf","tid":705670,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"一齊左兩年幾<br />\n乜都係我講佢做我問佢講<br />\n唔出聲就乜都唔會主動做<br />\n到忍唔住出聲既時候就話我唔合理<br />\n有啲問題由一齊第一個月講到而家e.g.唔好小小事就係街又喊又嘈<br />\n<br />\n岩先嘈交又自己係到發癲<br />\n本生都唔想理佢自己去沖涼<br />\n佢夠膽死我除哂衫黎開我門嘈<br />\n（廁所係露台，有人行過會望到哂）<br />\n之後我一路沖佢一直係外面打門+喊哂唔知講乜<br />\n次次發癲都話因為見到我嬲會好緊張所以先控制唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以教我應該點做"},{"pid":"01b2c15d0134dcb9fdece3eb0d34ec75fcff1ec3","tid":705670,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"咩事嘈交"},{"pid":"a2c84020d2009a9da3a8e763e9788c659de1e7dc","tid":705670,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"b6893639a26c85a66322e5f4bc585f9034b8e5c4","tid":705670,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"你都係想人叫你分手姐 分手啦"},{"pid":"550cd2befadcb29ad365394cba8fc3314e225934","tid":705670,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b2c15d0134dcb9fdece3eb0d34ec75fcff1ec3","tid":705670,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"咩事嘈交"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"琴晚發生左啲事但佢唔出聲幫下我<br />\n今日黎氹我，買左份禮物 但係佢既野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就話有咩理由你激嬲人但買自己野就算係你都是旦執樣比我啦<br />\n之後佢走去自己執屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f077bbfd19b2d17247f51ae59e26ee79cd0a9a9","tid":705670,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6893639a26c85a66322e5f4bc585f9034b8e5c4","tid":705670,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"你都係想人叫你分手姐 分手啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"有冇可能改變到<br />\n兩年唔長，但唔想咁易放棄"},{"pid":"4358b10179c6c8fae349d2be2252816ef4c1627e","tid":705670,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"好撚攰<br />\n乜都我講佢做好似自己同自己拍拖咁<br />\n佢又覺得我當佢係狗<br />\n<br />\n如果令到另一半唔開心既事都唔嘗試去理解下聽下改下<br />\n寧願由佢自己一個唔開心，咁一齊做乜"},{"pid":"9f90c68069089d0232e132995be1277e67b476ad","tid":705670,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5502c4951a1a048f1833309a2ee8f7065aa624","tid":705670,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"咁你分唔分手阿失婆"}]}